                              {bet.betType.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + bet.betType.slice(1)} ‚Ä¢ {bet.teamBet} ‚Ä¢ {formatOdds(bet.odds)}
                            </p>
                            <p className="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
